### create one Patient
POST http://localhost:5003/api/patients
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "first_name": "John",
  "last_name": "Doe",
  "email_address": "johnd@example.com",
  "password": "password123",
  "gender": "male",
  "phone_number": "12345678",
  "birth_date": "1990-01-01",
  "location": {
    "address": "123 Main St",
    "country": "USA",
    "city": "New York",
    "longitude": 40.7128,
    "latitude": -74.0060
  }
}

### update one Patient 
PUT http://localhost:5003/api/patients/645ac11d6bddc90a33ed26f5
